    <h1>Welcome to the Cricket World</h1>
    <p>Learn more about the sport of cricket, top teams, famous players, and amazing statistics!</p>
    <h2>What is Cricket?</h2>
    <p>Cricket is a bat-and-ball game played between two teams of eleven players each on a field at the center of which is a 22-yard pitch with a wicket at each end, each comprising two bails balanced on three stumps. The batting team scores runs by hitting the ball with the bat and running between the wickets, while the fielding team tries to dismiss the players (get them out) in various ways.</p>
