        <h2>Cricket Stats</h2>
        <p>Here are some of the top cricket records:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Most runs in ODI: <strong>Sachin Tendulkar</strong> with 18,426 runs</li>
            <li>Most wickets in Test: <strong>Muttiah Muralitharan</strong> with 800 wickets</li>
            <li>Fastest Century in ODI: <strong>AB de Villiers</strong> in 31 balls</li>
            <li>Most Sixes in an ODI: <strong>Shahid Afridi</strong> with 351 sixes</li>
        </ul>
